diff:1381960957:1381960510:=47,48c47%0a%3c *''Hunt Club (Vampires, Mortals)'': %0a%3c In life and in death, hunting has long been a past-time for Gideon Ward.  As a vampire, Gideon has so many more opportunities for quarry.  Whether for animals or kine, Gideon invites his fellow Kindred out for sport, and enjoys making a game of it.  Going "fox" hunting on stolen steeds or playing a friendly game of "tag" with .22 rifles are all Gideon's ideas of a good time.  Gideon has his limits, though--it's gauche to kill kine for sport.  Maybe you want to go hunting with Gideon, or maybe you end up quarry.%0a---%0a> *''Hunt Club (Vampires)'': %0a
