diff:1381960510:1381960349:=31d30%0a%3c %0a41,43c40,42%0a%3c *''Knight of the White Kamelia  (Mortals)'': %0a%3c Gideon maintains nothing so pretentious as an Invictus knighthood, but he has long been a knight of a different order: a circle of brothers dedicated to patriotism and purity.  Gideon keeps his secret closely, and interacts only at a distance, but it's possible others in respectable civic groups may feel his influence.%0a%3c %0a---%0a> *''Knight of the White Kamelia  (Mortals, Others)'': %0a> Gideon maintains nothing so pretentious as an Invictus knighthood, but he has long been a knight of a different order: a circle of brothers dedicated to patriotism and purity.  Gideon keeps his secret closely, and interacts only at a distance, but it's possible others in respect civic groups may feel his influence.%0a> %0a47,48c46%0a%3c *''Hunt Club (Vampires)'': %0a%3c %0a---%0a> *''Hook 3 (Applicable Group)'': %0a
