diff:1381875074:1381872249:=30c30%0a%3c ''Gideon Ward stands at an even six foot, but his presence looms larger.  His square jaw and and short blonde hair mark out a handsome face marred by an unsettling intensity in his pale blue eyes.  Gideon is perpetually dressed for business, typically in old-fashioned cuts with three-piece suits and peaked-lapel jackets.''%0a---%0a> ''Gideon ward stands at an even six foot, but his presence looms larger.  His square jaw and and short blonde hair mark out a handsome face marred by an unsettling intensity in his pale blue eyes.''%0a33,38c33,34%0a%3c ''Gideon Ward has stalked the streets of Savannah for nearly twenty years.  Genteel and capable, he quickly found a place in Kindred society.  When Gideon is not cultivating his own projects, he serves the Carthian Movement mentoring fledglings, mediating disputes, and clerking with the Senate.  Gideon has become known recently for pushing a social agenda of legal reform.  The proclamations of the Senate and the Prince, Ward says, are not sufficient to properly order society.  Kindred Society ought to adopt proper law for contracts and property, in addition to the Traditions and the old laws fiefdoms.''%0a%3c %0a%3c ''In Gideon's mortal days, now nearly thirty years past, the man was an upstanding man from a proud family.  At the apex of an enviable career, Judge Ward sat on the bench of the Georgia Court of Appeals, and was on the verge of an appointment to the Georgia Supreme Court.  But then Gideon Ward died.  %0a%3c %0a%3c Gideon spent the better part of the next ten years in Atlanta before returning to his native Savannah.[[%3c%3c]]%0a%3c %0a---%0a> ''Gideon Ward has stalked the streets of Savannah for nearly twenty years.  Genteel and capable, he quickly found a place in Kindred society.  When Gideon is not cultivating his own projects, he serves the Carthian Movement mentoring fledglings, mediating disputes, and clerking with the Senate.''%0a> [[%3c%3c]]%0a
